room_title: Escape room "Key to the Throne" by Game the Room in Rohnert Park
room_address: 5430 Commerce Blvd Suite 2G Rohnert Park, CA 94928
room_description: You have infiltrated the castle of the oppressive House Wrathion. Your kingdom is losing the war against the Wrathions, but there is a prophecy that the enemies of Wrathion will win the war if they can steal one of their dragon eggs. You have one hour to find the dragon egg, escape the stronghold, and turn the tides of war!
